rowdfunding Plan<br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=56e13592\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=c209c9ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二、什麼是遊說集團？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n遊說集團的工作，<strong><ins>是嘗試影響立法者</ins></strong>或其他持份者決定或行為，在政治角力中為服務對象<strong><ins>爭取利益</ins></strong>。遊說集團的服務對象，可以是國家、企業、社會團體、個人。在美國，政治遊說是極為普遍及重要的一環；幾乎所有政治操作都有遊說集團的參與。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">三、為什麼香港需要遊說隊伍？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n任何國家的政治，背後都擁有複雜的政治脈絡；包括國家政策、政治形勢、民意、錯綜複雜的利益網絡、乃至個別官員或議員的性情喜好。要在國際社會維護和爭取香港的利益，<strong><ins>香港需要一支能具經驗和技巧，能夠有效收風、熟識政治形勢</ins></strong>、具備遊說策略的隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">四、遊說集團？對家一早做緊啊！</span></span></strong><br />\n【華為被禁】華為遊說費飆60倍！原來聘用特朗普籌款人 欲說服白宮<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2479940%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=f304e6e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2479940?r=cpsdlc</a><br />\n<br />\n董建華基金會 擲2,240萬左右美政策<br />\n大搞政治游說 否認中共代理人<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=991a8585\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171130%2F20230175&h=11b362ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171130/20230175</a>"},{"pid":"6d10e65466e93d69ab8e4e47986ad1c8f5802f8b","tid":1672342,"uid":10844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:54:37.000Z","msg":"估唔到仲有人上yahoo"},{"pid":"012d624bab60cfaf21fd99bef597ea645531bd25","tid":1672342,"uid":216878,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6d10e65466e93d69ab8e4e47986ad1c8f5802f8b","tid":1672342,"uid":10844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:54:37.000Z","msg":"估唔到仲有人上yahoo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:51:53.000Z","msg":"慣咗, 以前一有電腦就set佢做首頁.<br />\n以前學校電腦, 同學屋企都係set呢個做首頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n依家佢個網啲新聞下面好撚多5毛回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />."},{"pid":"f7759d5c4fa3065c46ac256cebe701c3f0133ef5","tid":1672342,"uid":241520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T15:53:58.000Z","msg":"2TB 定2GB usb🤔🤔"},{"pid":"c0799af671ced0b3a08aed93b929ac8b4d6e1725","tid":1672342,"uid":216878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7759d5c4fa3065c46ac256cebe701c3f0133ef5","tid":1672342,"uid":241520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT